{"id":492,"date":"2021-02-24T14:44:54","date_gmt":"2021-02-24T14:44:54","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/malibuvalleyrealty.com\/?page_id=492"},"modified":"2021-04-09T22:14:09","modified_gmt":"2021-04-09T22:14:09","slug":"about-malibu-valley-estates","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/malibuvalley.com\/about\/about-malibu-valley-estates\/","title":{"rendered":"Malibu Valley"},"content":{"rendered":"<div  style='padding-bottom:10px; ' class='av-special-heading av-special-heading-h3  blockquote elegant-quote elegant-centered  avia-builder-el-0  el_before_av_section  avia-builder-el-no-sibling  avia-font-fontello '><h3 class='av-special-heading-tag '  itemprop=\"headline\"  ><span class=\"heading-wrap\">About Malibu Valley<\/span><\/h3><div class='special-heading-border'><div class='special-heading-inner-border' ><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><!-- close content main div --><\/div><\/div><div id='full-slider'  class='avia-section main_color avia-section-default avia-no-border-styling  avia-bg-style-scroll  avia-builder-el-1  el_after_av_heading  el_before_av_one_fifth   container_wrap fullsize' style=' '  ><div class='container' ><div class='template-page content  av-content-full alpha units'><div class='post-entry post-entry-type-page post-entry-492'><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix'>\n\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><!-- close content main div --><\/div><\/div><div id='after_section_1'  class='main_color av_default_container_wrap container_wrap fullsize' style=' '  ><div class='container' ><div class='template-page content  av-content-full alpha units'><div class='post-entry post-entry-type-page post-entry-492'><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix'>\n<div class=\"flex_column av_one_fifth  flex_column_div av-zero-column-padding first  avia-builder-el-3  el_after_av_section  el_before_av_three_fifth  avia-builder-el-first  \" style='border-radius:0px; '><\/div>\n<div class=\"flex_column av_three_fifth  flex_column_div   avia-builder-el-4  el_after_av_one_fifth  el_before_av_one_fifth  \" style='padding:12px; border-radius:2px; '><section class=\"av_textblock_section \"  itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/CreativeWork\" ><div class='avia_textblock  '   itemprop=\"text\" ><h3>Malibu Valley<\/h3>\n<p><span class=\"drop_cap\">M<\/span>alibu Valley presents a remarkable opportunity to own an estate property on the edge of one of the world\u2019s most vibrant cities.<\/p>\n<p>A private gated enclave of 26 homes situated on approximately 100 acres nestled within the Santa Monica Mountains, Malibu Valley includes the ultimate in new construction. Homes range from 6,000 to 11,000 square feet, each with its own architectural style. Each home has luxury, premiere finishes along with individualized designer touches, including imported marble, hand painted tiles, luxury appliances, handcrafted finishes and Crestron automation.<\/p>\n<p>Malibu Valley Estates also offers the rare opportunity to purchase a Lot and design your own dream home. Extraordinary approvals allow for 50-foot height limits, increased wall and fence heights and almost limitless design freedom.<\/p>\n<h3>Climate<\/h3>\n<p><span class=\"drop_cap\">O<\/span>nly 3% of the world has a Mediterranean Climate, characterized by dry summers and mild winters. And even in those few places, there are limited opportunities where you can surf and ski in the same day, be in close proximity to boating, off-roading, mountain biking and horseback riding on hundreds of miles of trails. Imagine having breakfast on a snow-covered mountain, lunch in a desert oasis and dinner on the beach while watching the sunset in one jaw-dropping day. Malibu Valley is that one spectacular place \u2013 your home base to explore and experience everything Southern California has to offer.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/section><\/div>\n<div class=\"flex_column av_one_fifth  flex_column_div av-zero-column-padding   avia-builder-el-6  el_after_av_three_fifth  avia-builder-el-